1.DownLoad the repository
2.open build.gradle add httpPort:"port number" in "gretty {}" section
3.add proxy settings in gradle.wrapper.properties
4.run command "gradle buildProduct"
5.change the name of haystack-snapshot.war to haystack-java.war
6.try building again
7.Copy the contents of build/output/ into conatiner directory
8.goto container directory write a Dockerfile and build the image
9.Run the image
10.Push the image to the docker hub
